flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Daily inventory data update from SAP S/4HANA.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Extract inventory data from SAP S/4HANA.]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Analyze inventory turns and days of supply.]
  N2 --> N3[Cortex: RCA Service - Perform root cause analysis on inventory discrepancies.]
  N3 --> N4{PB: CWB Lifecycle - Recommend and implement process improvements.}
  N4 -->|Primary| N5[PB: Notification - Notify stakeholders of findings and actions.]
  N5 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced carrying costs, minimized stockouts, improved COGS, and enhanced overall inventory health.]
  N4 -->|Significant inventory discrepancy det...| B1[Initiate root cause analysis.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Corrective actions identified and implemented.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N4 -->|High carrying costs identified.| B2[Propose policy changes.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Policy adjustments made to reduce costs.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N4 -->|No actionable process improvements fo...| B3[Continue monitoring.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Maintain current inventory processes.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]